ğŸ³ **Docker**
- `docker ps -a` â€“ List all containers
- `docker images` â€“ List all images
- `docker run -d -p 8080:80 nginx` â€“ Run nginx container
- `docker exec -it <id> bash` â€“ Shell into container
- `docker build -t app .` â€“ Build image from Dockerfile
- `docker-compose up -d` â€“ Run containers in background
